room_title: Escape room "The Green Room" by Lock & Clue Escape Rooms in Providence
room_description: Congratulations! You won a chance to appear on “Natural Selection”, a live-streaming web series. You don’t know what the show is about, but you were told it has a cult following and you get to relax in the star lounge before the show. What fun! But, there’s something much darker going on here. You have an hour to get to the bottom of it. Fifteen minutes of fame isn’t worth much if you’re not around to enjoy it!
